## 6. 命名规范 (revive)

### 接口命名避免口吃

```go
// ❌ BAD - 在 executor 包中定义 ExecutorRegistry
package executor
type ExecutorRegistry interface { /* ... */ }
// 使用时：executor.ExecutorRegistry（口吃）

// ✅ GOOD - 简化命名
package executor
type Registry interface { /* ... */ }
// 使用时：executor.Registry（简洁）
```

### 导出常量需要注释

```go
// ❌ BAD
const DefaultRetryLimit = 3

// ✅ GOOD
// DefaultRetryLimit is the default maximum number of retry attempts
const DefaultRetryLimit = 3

// ✅ GOOD - 常量块注释
// Retry configuration constants
const (
    // DefaultRetryLimit is the default maximum number of retry attempts
    DefaultRetryLimit = 3
    // DefaultRetryInterval is the default initial retry interval
    DefaultRetryInterval = 5 * time.Second
)
```

